    Na'vi River Journey Wait Times

    navi_river.Rd

    A dataset containing Na'vi River Journey wait times.

    navi_river

    Format

    A data frame with 182,121 rows and 4 variables:

    date

    Park Day (not actual date stamp of the wait time, since some are after midnight), Date

    datetime

    date-time stamp of wait time, YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM:SS

    wait_minutes_actual

    Actual Wait Time (in minutes), numeric

    wait_minutes_posted

    Standby Posted Wait Time (in minutes), numeric

    Source

    "navi_river.csv" Disney World Ride Wait Time Datasets, TouringPlans.com, August 2023, https://touringplans.com/walt-disney-world/crowd-calendar#DataSets, Accessed 28 August 2023
